的重大節日、重要慶典或其他社會活動時，均經常穿着軍服。軍服是軍人身分的象徵，駐港部隊人員穿着軍服出席公眾場合，不僅可增強榮譽感和使命感，亦能令市民更加認識駐港部隊。他們的合法行為和公益服務，應獲得我們尊重和支持。<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.info.gov.hk/gia/general/201811/28/P2018112800413.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.info.gov.hk%2Fgia%2Fgeneral%2F201811%2F28%2FP2018112800413.htm&d=x8osXdNjm17U7TcHCf5EXo26uSpwD1fkwqqc2qDkc5E%3D&h=7e44647b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.info.gov.hk/gia/general/201811/28/P2018112800413.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n咁即係佢地而家<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">代表緊解放軍出動</span></span>, 要<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">推俾美國睇</span></span>!!!!!!!!!"},{"pid":"2e223bccdb0114f73c3d176f0129417b4ca0f663","tid":1726930,"uid":131122,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"f174122deb9bc9fb92126a2040b6b606224cd298","tid":1726930,"uid":16676,"like":12,"dislike":2,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T09:55:14.000Z","msg":"吐露港通返車即刻乘勝追擊, 再下一城<br />\n大膽到連老解都出黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n休息L <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T10:48:01.000Z","msg":"撤係無問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f03e77f6fc6b2c7f2d3b35efe84154c9da4fe71e","tid":1726930,"uid":283040,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2139872d7a02f88e4ee125b46d7668151df8812c","tid":1726930,"uid":89752,"like":41,"dislike":0,"score":41,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T09:52:04.000Z","msg":"諗番當日，佢話619之後即刻撤回，交3，5個人出黎祭旗，影響仲少過7警<br />\n<br />\n到而家咁樣大龍鳳收科，咁多血債，個人覺得好唏噓"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T10:48:12.000Z","msg":"當初五個告暴動都告唔成啦<br />\n<br />\n成班無腦愛面子害死香港人"},{"pid":"43faaa5036e241af3a813ab6a99989321f3e36a1","tid":